  "reviewNotes": [
    "F3/F4/F10 splice metadata is recorded only; physical couplers are not created by this tool version.",
    "Bottom layer centre offsets are explicit from the drawing/user review: F4=220, F3=247, F6=320, F5=347 mm from bottom face to bar centre.",
    "Split piece X-length callouts are developed/cut lengths; straightLengthMm stores the actual horizontal segment shown by the dimension line.",
    "F7/F8/F10 placement grids are seeded from the detail images and should be checked against the target host orientation before production use.",
    "Only 180-degree hooks use native RebarHookType. 90-degree hooks from the images are modeled as explicit line legs so their rotation is controlled."
  ]
